<!-- ====================================================================== 
   El calentamiento es un <exploration> (distinto a las otras actividades)
   Para RRRRR usar el estilo del calentamiento. Por ejemplo, usar 
   RRRRRR=observa con los "Observa y Pregúntate"
===========================================================================  -->
<exploration xml:id="warm-converNum-masGruposMenosGrupos" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"> 

<title>[@@@@@@@@@]</title>

<statement>
  <p>[@@@@@@@@@]</p>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <ul>
      <li>35: because I counted by 5 like 5, 10, 15, 20, 25, 30, 35. I just knew it.</li>
      <li>28: because there would be 4 groups of 7 instead of 5. So, 35 minus 7 would be 28.</li>
      <li>42: because there would be one more group of 7 than in the first problem. So, 35 plus 7 would be 42.</li>
      <li>32: because there would be one less group of 8 than <m>5 \times 8</m>. So 40 minus 8 would be 32.</li>
    </ul>
  </solution>


